      '&lt;h2>&lt;strong>Call for Papers: 8th Global Conference on Pharmacy &amp; Pharmaceutical Science&lt;/strong>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>The 8th edition of the Global Conference on Pharmacy &amp; Pharmaceutical Science invites researchers, industry professionals, and scholars to submit their latest research contributions. This international conference in Vancouver, Canada provides a prestigious platform to present findings, discuss innovations, and collaborate on advancements in pharmacy and pharmaceutical sciences.&lt;/p>&lt;p>Submissions are welcomed in areas such as drug formulation and development, clinical pharmacy advancements, digital transformation in healthcare, pharmacovigilance, and regulatory science. Every paper will undergo a rigorous double-blind peer review process to ensure high academic and industry standards.&lt;/p>&lt;p>Join the conversation, contribute to pharmaceutical advancements, and network with global experts. Submit your research and make an impact at this renowned international pharmacy conference in Canada.&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>&lt;strong style="color: rgb(214, 34, 41);">Topics of interest include, but are not limited to:&lt;/strong>Advances in Drug Development&lt;/li>&lt;li>Clinical Pharmacy and Patient Care&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmaceutical Technology and Nanomedicine&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmacovigilance and Drug Safety&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmacoeconomics and Health Policy&lt;/li>&lt;li>Regulatory Affairs in Pharmaceuticals&lt;/li>&lt;li>Biopharmaceuticals and Personalized Medicine&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmacy Education and Ethics&lt;/li>&lt;li>Digital Health and Telepharmacy&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmaceutical Research Methodologies&lt;/li>&lt;li>Community Pharmacy and Public Health&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmacogenomics and Precision Medicine&lt;/li>&lt;li>Innovations in Drug Delivery Systems&lt;/li>&lt;li>Global Health and Access to Medications&lt;/li>&lt;li>Impact of Pandemics on Pharmaceutical Practices&lt;/li>&lt;li>Medication Therapy Management&lt;/li>&lt;li>Antimicrobial Stewardship&lt;/li>&lt;li>Pharmaceutical Compounding and Formulation&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>&lt;p>&lt;br>&lt;/p>',
